title: $4740-4/3 Pembroke Pines 2 Story Home-Immaculate-Lake View-Pet Ok

posting_body: ['Spacious 4/3 with a 2 car garage and a loft in the gated community of Victoria Lakes.', '1 bedroom and a full bath on the first floor.', 'The property is freshly painted, and it offers a fenced-in backyard for privacy.', 'The kitchen has brand new appliances and brand new washer & dryer, upgraded cabinets & granite counter tops.', 'Laminated wood floors in all living and other areas.', 'Huge formal living/dining rooms and a separate family area.', 'The Master bedroom has a built-in closet, and the bathroom has his & her sink area with a huge tub.', 'This community is conveniently located in the heart of Pembroke Pines, close to shopping centers, good schools, parks, restaurants, and major highways.', 'Rare availability in this community.', 'This is A must-see!', 'Amazing community pool !!!', 'Pets under 20 Lbs only.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease (650+), background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
